@startuml 3B_Fan_Content_Upload
title 3-B · Media Gallery Upload & Fan Access (UC-T16, UC-F18, UC-F19)

start
|Tenant Admin (Owner/Admin)|
:Open Media Gallery manager;
:Choose media files and enter\nalbum/item title, description and visibility;

|System|
:Verify tenant status = ACTIVE;
:Validate file size, type and storage quota;
if (Validation passed?) then (No)
  :Return validation or plan error;
  stop
else (Yes)
  :Upload media to storage;
  :Create MediaGallery / MediaItem records;
  :Save visibility level\n(PUBLIC / SUBSCRIBERS_ONLY / PAID_ONLY);
  :Invalidate fansite cache;
endif

|Anonymous Visitor / Registered Fan|
:Browse media galleries;

|System|
:Load visible galleries for tenant;
if (Gallery requires subscription?) then (Yes)
  if (Fan has active subscription/tier?) then (No)
    :Show locked preview and subscription prompt;
    stop
  else (Yes)
    :Allow gallery access;
  endif
else (No)
  :Allow public gallery access;
endif

|Anonymous Visitor / Registered Fan|
:Open a media item;
|System|
:Render media item and metadata;
stop
@enduml
